{"id": "1421875137300398090", "channel_id": "1181152750319456266", "author_id": "1146484628912353451", "author_name": "wqin.", "content": "好討厭啊，我媽為什麼還要十幾天才要去工作呢", "timestamp": "2025-09-28T15:04:09.895000+00:00"}
{"id": "1421875179440836780", "channel_id": "1181152750319456266", "author_id": "1146484628912353451", "author_name": "wqin.", "content": "有點難以忍受了", "timestamp": "2025-09-28T15:04:19.942000+00:00"}
{"id": "1421875259086475316", "channel_id": "1181152750319456266", "author_id": "1146484628912353451", "author_name": "wqin.", "content": "感覺在過三天我就能精神崩潰了呢", "timestamp": "2025-09-28T15:04:38.931000+00:00"}
{"id": "1421875303638241492", "channel_id": "1181152750319456266", "author_id": "1146484628912353451", "author_name": "wqin.", "content": "<:stare:1400771751650136145>", "timestamp": "2025-09-28T15:04:49.553000+00:00"}
{"id": "1421875409225650237", "channel_id": "1181152750319456266", "author_id": "1146484628912353451", "author_name": "wqin.", "content": "把我房間堆滿他的東西變成垃圾場了", "timestamp": "2025-09-28T15:05:14.727000+00:00"}
{"id": "1421875533066665994", "channel_id": "1181152750319456266", "author_id": "1146484628912353451", "author_name": "wqin.", "content": "把我的零食櫃吃空了", "timestamp": "2025-09-28T15:05:44.253000+00:00"}
{"id": "1421875594211102720", "channel_id": "1181152750319456266", "author_id": "1146484628912353451", "author_name": "wqin.", "content": "把我房間的冷氣用壞了", "timestamp": "2025-09-28T15:05:58.831000+00:00"}
{"id": "1421875712389808312", "channel_id": "1181152750319456266", "author_id": "1146484628912353451", "author_name": "wqin.", "content": "睡覺翻身還會攻擊我，或是壓縮我的生存空間", "timestamp": "2025-09-28T15:06:27.007000+00:00"}
{"id": "1421875762729848903", "channel_id": "1181152750319456266", "author_id": "1146484628912353451", "author_name": "wqin.", "content": "做什麼事都要被罵，被唸", "timestamp": "2025-09-28T15:06:39.009000+00:00"}
{"id": "1421875902459154495", "channel_id": "1181152750319456266", "author_id": "1146484628912353451", "author_name": "wqin.", "content": "而且他還因為自己太熱而脫掉褲子穿內褲睡覺", "timestamp": "2025-09-28T15:07:12.323000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-09-28T15:07:39.570000+00:00"}
{"id": "1421875920037351455", "channel_id": "1181152750319456266", "author_id": "1146484628912353451", "author_name": "wqin.", "content": "這個我沒意見", "timestamp": "2025-09-28T15:07:16.514000+00:00"}
{"id": "1421875991885643817", "channel_id": "1181152750319456266", "author_id": "1146484628912353451", "author_name": "wqin.", "content": "但是那是在非我房間我才沒意見", "timestamp": "2025-09-28T15:07:33.644000+00:00"}
{"id": "1421876280860741632", "channel_id": "1181152750319456266", "author_id": "1146484628912353451", "author_name": "wqin.", "content": "而且他還一堆神奇操作(感覺頭腦在跳，血壓有點高)", "timestamp": "2025-09-28T15:08:42.541000+00:00"}
{"id": "1421877663340957890", "channel_id": "1181152750319456266", "author_id": "1146484628912353451", "author_name": "wqin.", "content": "他睡不著還喜歡觀察我，晚上睡覺有時迷迷糊糊翻個身直接跟我媽貼臉而且他還睜大眼睛在看我欸", "timestamp": "2025-09-28T15:14:12.150000+00:00"}
{"id": "1421877913459888209", "channel_id": "1181152750319456266", "author_id": "1146484628912353451", "author_name": "wqin.", "content": "而且每天都在給我施壓增加壓力，而且還害我沒安全感", "timestamp": "2025-09-28T15:15:11.783000+00:00"}
{"id": "1421877992132706405", "channel_id": "1181152750319456266", "author_id": "1146484628912353451", "author_name": "wqin.", "content": "他回來這個月我頭髮已經比平常多掉兩把了", "timestamp": "2025-09-28T15:15:30.540000+00:00"}
